org.openmap4u.canvas

Interface DrawOrWriteable

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    SetAreaOfInterestOrDrawOrWriteable

    public interface DrawOrWriteable
    Allow either to draw another primitive on the canvas, or to write the result to the provided output stream.
    Author:
    Michael Hadrbolec
